NanaDIY & MomDIY 🥺❤️

Back to LA this week! I want to personally thank every single person who has gotten vaccinated. You’re the reason that I, and so many other families are able to reunite after countless long and emotionally exhausting months. Thank you thank you thank you ❤️.
